data.description: Welcome to this ranch home in Kettering sitting on a nice fenced in lot on the end of a quiet street with no thru traffic. The home boasts over 2,500 square feet with 5 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a two-car attached garage. Recent updates include new electric panel by A-Abel (2023), new water heater (2023), new carpet (April 2022), new HVAC system (2018), roof and siding (2012), new gutters and downspouts (2015), laminate vinyl plank flooring in several rooms, and the hallway bathroom is updated. The garage is heated with a 220 V Heater. The home is located close to the 675, The Greene shopping and entertainment center, a short drive to WPAFB, restaurants and shopping.
